<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.187421>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Polyzoa atlantica n. sp. A and B a colony consisting of several zooids attached to the test of the solitary ascidian Molgula occidentalis. C zooids separated from the substrate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/187421/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.187423>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Polyzoa atlantica n. sp. A zooid opened ventrally; branchial sac removed to show gonads, endocarps, and gut loop. B Gut loop of another zooid. C Tailed larva." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/187423/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

